strings: <voice_0x01001472><se_def>Awesome!: About us Have we met somewhere?
<voice_0x01001473><se_def>China: Brother, how much have you stolen from me?
<voice_0x01001474><se_def>Awesome!: That's right! Due to repeated violations of the rules, he was expelled from the monastery.
<voice_0x01001476><se_def>Awesome!: Wow, so beautiful! I hope it won't hurt.
<voice_0x01001477><se_def>Awesome!: But I don't have time to wait. Someone had to be selected as the high priest's bodyguard.
<voice_0x01001478><se_def>Awesome!: I cannot bear a carefree life like yours. so please forgive me
<voice_0x01001479><se_def>Awesome!: Everything is fine, and God bless you.
<voice_0x0100147A><se_def>*: marry! How could a person like him command the High Priest Guards?
<voice_0x0100147B><se_def>*: An important quest that demands fame! Someone with the same personality as you and me.
<voice_0x0100147C><se_def>*: There is no question that this monk bribed His Majesty. I've heard a rumor about it.
<voice_0x0100147D><se_def>*: It does not last long and only serves as a protective barrier. He is happy when he gets a raise.
<voice_0x0100147E><se_def>*: Then use money. The weight of his meager contribution immediately brought him back to reality.
